--General speech
 
"Hello","Greetings","Be greeted","Hail","Good day","Good morning","Good evening"->"Ah, you must be the deliverer of marble. Put it just next to the stack of bricks.","Welcome, stranger. Do you have any building material for me?","Be greeted, in the name of the queen."
"Grüße","Gruß","Seid gegrüßt","Guten Tag","Guten Abend","Mahlzeit","Tach","Moin"->"Ah, ihr müßt der Marmorlieferant sein. Lagert es neben den Ziegelsteinen.","Willkommen, Fremdling. Habt ihr Baumaterial für mich?","Seid im Namen der Königin gegrüßt."
"Hiho","Hallo","Hey","Greebas","Greebs",english->"Ah, you must be the deliverer of marble. Put it just next to the stack of bricks.","Welcome, stranger. Do you have any building material for me?","Be greeted, in the name of the queen."
"Hiho","Hallo","Hey","Greebas","Greebs",german->"Auf wiedersehen.","Bis zum nächsten mal.","Gehet in Frieden."
"Farewell","Good bye","Bye","Fare thy well"->"Farewell.","Good bye.","Until next time."
"Tschüß","Tschüss","Wiedersehen","Gehabt euch wohl"->"Auf wiedersehen.","Bis zum nächsten mal.","Gehet in Frieden."
"Ciao","Adieu","Au revoir",english->"Farewell.","Good bye.","Until next time."
"Ciao","Adieu","Au revoir",german->"Auf wiedersehen.","Bis zum nächsten mal.","Gehet in Frieden."
"How are you","How feel","How do you do"->"As long as the queen is content, I am happy. And I do anything to please her.","I just need to finish this calculation, then we can talk.","Every day is a day to serve queen Rosaline."
"Wie geht","Wie fühlst","Wie ist es ergangen"->"Solange die Königin zufrieden ist, bin ich es auch. Und ich werde alles tun, um sie zufrieden zu stellen.","Ich muss nur noch grad diese Berechnung abschließen, dann können wir reden.","Jeder Tag ist der richtige, um Königin Rosaline zu dienen."
"your name","who are you","who art thou"->"Robertus.","My name is Robertus, I am the royal builder. I serve the queen with every fibre of my body.","They call me Robertus. I'm the royal builder of Cadomyr, loyal to the queen."
"dein name","wer bist du","wer seid ihr","wie heißt"->"Robertus.","Mein Name ist Robertus, ich bin der königliche Baumeister. Ich diene der Königin mit jeder Faser meines Körpers.","Man nennt mich Robertus. Ich bin der königliche Baumeister Cadomyrs, stets der Königin ergeben."

--Catching typical NPC phrases

"what sell","what buy","list wares","price of"->"I trade building materials. I'll purchase anything that can help building her majesty's... place of peaceful rest.","Bricks, stone blocks, marble... I trade all the workers need.","I can sell you the tools you need to serve the queen. On, on!"
"was verkauf","was kauf","warenliste","preis von"->"Ich handele mit Baumaterialien. Ich werde alles erwerben, was benötigt wird um für ihre Majestät... einen Ort der letzten Ruhe zu bauen.","Ziegelsteine, Steinblöcke, Marmor... Ich handele mit allem, was die Arbeiter brauchen.","Ich kann euch die Werkzeuge verkaufen, die ihr braucht, um Königin Rosaline zu dienen. Los, los!"
"tell something"->"Shh, don't speak about this in public, but we're actually building the queen's grave.","I wonder where all the refugees came from. More hands for the queen!","Never venture to the mountains alone. Dragons were reported to roam there."
"erzähl was","erzähl etwas"->"Shh, redet nicht davon in der Öffentlichkeit, aber wir bauen das Grab der Königin","Ich frage mich nur, wo die Flüchtlinge alle herkamen. Ach, mehr Hände für die Königin!","Wagt es niemals, alleine in die Berge zu gehen. Angeblich treiben dort Drachen ihr Unwesen."

